            .section#section-kids
                .kids
                    h2
                        i.icon.child
                        | Kids
                    .kids-content
                        p Many of our friends have beautiful children, whom we would love to share our day with. Please feel free to bring the little ones along to the ceremony / drinks & canapés reception. We hope to hold it outside (weather permitting) so there should be plenty of space for them to move and play throughout the day.
                        p For the evening dinner celebrations we plan to hold an adult-only event. This is mostly due to limited space, but also allows all guests an evening of relaxation, without having to worry about little eyes and ears. We hope that this advance notice means that you are still able to share our big day with us and that you can enjoy the evening off parental duties.
                        p Our wedding planner has organised many childfree weddings, working with a properly vetted and tested nanny agency called SillyBillies. They are an English speaking agency who have been police checked and ID verified. We understand that some guests may feel uncomfortable about leaving their little one, so we totally understand that this may not work for you.
                        p We will be providing a baby sitting agency in the lounge room of the chateau, so please let us know if you wish to utilize this service (as the ratio of sitters to kids will be affected and we need to organize enough sitters ahead of time.)
                        p If you want to organize the sitter to come to your accommodation, you can also do that privately at a cost of 25euros booking fee per sitter, then 15euro per hour, per sitter. Min of 4 hours.  (ALL TBC)
                        p 
                            |You can visit the agency’s website 
                            a(href="http://www.sillybillyschildcare.com/", target="_new") here 
                            |, or you can get in touch with the owner of the agency directly to discuss your requirements. Her name is Nicci Brown and her email address is 
                            a(href="mailto:sillybillynicci@aol.com") sillybillynicci@aol.com
                            |.
                        
            .section#section-gifts
                h1
                    i.icon.gift
                    | Gifts
                .gifts
                    .gifts-content
                        p We know that flights and accommodation can become very expensive and we are so grateful that you are willing to travel to be with us on our special day. We truly believe that your presence at our celebration is a beautiful gift for us to treasure and so, no others are needed, Thank You.
                        p For those who insist on giving something- Please send or email us a photograph, once you get home, of yourselves enjoying France in all it’s beautiful cheese and wine glory, so that we have a beautiful memento of our special tribe. :)

